WorkItem.Description:
It is great that PHPExcel is now supporting superscript / subscript! Still there may be minor quirks? Not sure what is causing this, but please check attached test files. Everything before the super- or subscript seems to lose formatting after a plain read/write using Excel2007 reader/writer?
 
Code snippet:
---
$reader = new PHPExcel_Reader_Excel2007();
$PHPExcel = $reader->load('2007-read.xlsx');
$writer = new PHPExcel_Writer_Excel2007($PHPExcel);
$writer->save('2007-write.xlsx');
 
Environment: Latest source from SVN (1.6.3+)
